{"tid":1109412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"問「我靚唔靚」沒反應 妻子發狂怒打丈夫被捕","createTime":"2019-04-16T09:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T09:19:04.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d155f672ffdaf5e23b906d772d61a2fc4bcb58f","tid":1109412,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"美國德州拉雷多鎮發生一宗奇特家暴事件。一名女子問丈夫她是否美麗，但丈夫沒反應，她竟勃然大怒，動粗打丈夫，事後被警方拘捕及控以傷人罪。<br />\n<br />\n警方於上周二晚接到有人報案，說發生暴力傷人案。警員到場調查時，20歲女事主拉米雷茲（Lizeth Guadalupe Ramirez）聲稱自己被人打。不過，她的丈夫講出另一個版本，指2人看完電影駕車返家途中，拉米雷茲問他「她是否美麗？」他聽不到及沒有作出反應，拉米雷茲便大發雷霆，在車上向他動粗。<br />\n<br />\n2人返抵家門時，拉米雷茲推開他及再動手打他。一名親人上前想分開他們時，都同樣被打。<br />\n<br />\n拉米雷茲被控以2項傷人罪和家暴罪名，獲准以1.6萬美元（約12.5萬港元）保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190415/_2019041518382765665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190415%2F_2019041518382765665.jpg&h=038c2adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/980314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F980314&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FMwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=58832277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F980314&h=3b6f8d16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/980314</a>"},{"pid":"c3804f1b70c538204090374b2a1edad5b68dd4ed","tid":1109412,"uid":11289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"咁既專用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點好意思問既 唔撚答你咪就算俾面你囉"},{"pid":"3d94f65719ee426ab410b13940ca1a449f7c8621","tid":1109412,"uid":11289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3804f1b70c538204090374b2a1edad5b68dd4ed","tid":1109412,"uid":11289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-